Instructions for working with data

Made two scripts to quickly set up XMM-Newton SAS environment:

    atran@treble:/data/mpofls/atran/research/xmm$ source sasinit

    sasversion:- Executing (routine): sasversion  -w 1 -V 4
    sasversion:- sasversion (sasversion-1.2)  [xmmsas_20141104_1833-14.0.0]
    started:  2015-09-24T15:37:56.000
    sasversion:- XMM-Newton SAS release and build information:

    SAS release: xmmsas_20141104_1833-14.0.0
    Compiled on: Tue Nov  4 19:11:59 GMT 2014
    Compiled by: sasbuild@sasbld02.net4.lan
    Platform   : RHEL5.8 64

    SAS-related environment variables that are set:

    SAS_DIR = /soft/XMM/xmmsas_20141104_1833
    SAS_PATH = /soft/XMM/xmmsas_20141104_1833

    sasversion:- sasversion (sasversion-1.2)  [xmmsas_20141104_1833-14.0.0] ended:
    2015-09-24T15:37:56.000

    Do not forget to define SAS_CCFPATH, SAS_CCF and SAS_ODF

    atran@treble:/data/mpofls/atran/research/xmm$ source sas_setpaths 0087940201

